6.5 LaTeX packages
Sometimes, you need to use some LaTeX packages to customize your document. To use those, you can add the following in the YAML:
preamble: |
  \biboptions{authoryear}
  \usepackage{url}
  \usepackage{pdflscape}
  \usepackage{float}
  \usepackage{booktabs}
  \usepackage{longtable}
  \usepackage{makecell}
  \usepackage{multirow}
